-- Gold for Immediate Delivery Declines After Three-Day Rally; Silver Falls
-- B y   W e n d y   P u g h
-- 2010-12-28T23:11:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/gold-for-immediate-delivery-declines-after-three-day-rally-silver-falls.html
Gold for immediate delivery fell 65
cents to $1,405.25 an ounce at 10:09 a.m. Melbourne time after
gaining for the past three days. The metal rose as much as 1.7
percent yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
